<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>心脏 on Aloha's Blog</title><link>https://daisilia.com/tags/%E5%BF%83%E8%84%8F/</link><description>Recent content in 心脏 on Aloha's Blog</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>zh-cn</language><lastBuildDate>Sat, 19 Nov 2022 14:26:40 +0800</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://daisilia.com/tags/%E5%BF%83%E8%84%8F/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>心力衰竭</title><link>https://daisilia.com/series/%E5%86%85%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6/%E5%BE%AA%E7%8E%AF%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85/%E5%BF%83%E5%8A%9B%E8%A1%B0%E7%AB%AD/</link><pubDate>Sat, 19 Nov 2022 14:11:20 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://daisilia.com/series/%E5%86%85%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6/%E5%BE%AA%E7%8E%AF%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85/%E5%BF%83%E5%8A%9B%E8%A1%B0%E7%AB%AD/</guid><description>&lt;dl>
&lt;dt>心力衰竭（heart failure）| 心衰&lt;/dt>
&lt;dd>各种心脏结构或功能性疾病导致心室充盈和（或）射血功能受损，心输出量不能满足机体组织代谢需求，以&lt;strong>肺循环和（或）体循环淤血&lt;/strong>，器官、组织血流灌注不足为临床表现的一组综合征，主要表现为&lt;em>呼吸困难&lt;/em>、&lt;em>体力活动受限&lt;/em>和&lt;em>体液潴留&lt;/em>。&lt;/dd>
&lt;dd>一般所说的心力衰竭即指慢性心力衰竭。&lt;/dd>
&lt;/dl>
&lt;p>&lt;a href="https://daisilia.com/series/%E7%97%85%E7%90%86%E7%94%9F%E7%90%86%E5%AD%A6/%E5%BF%83%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E4%B8%8D%E5%85%A8/">&lt;em>&lt;strong>心功能不全&lt;/strong>&lt;/em>&lt;/a>（cardiac dysfunction）或&lt;em>心功能障碍&lt;/em>理论上是一个更为广泛的概念，伴有&lt;strong>临床症状&lt;/strong>的心功能不全称为心力衰竭。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>心律失常</title><link>https://daisilia.com/series/%E5%86%85%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6/%E5%BE%AA%E7%8E%AF%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85/%E5%BF%83%E5%BE%8B%E5%A4%B1%E5%B8%B8/</link><pubDate>Sat, 19 Nov 2022 14:21:27 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://daisilia.com/series/%E5%86%85%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6/%E5%BE%AA%E7%8E%AF%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85/%E5%BF%83%E5%BE%8B%E5%A4%B1%E5%B8%B8/</guid><description/></item><item><title>心肌疾病</title><link>https://daisilia.com/series/%E5%86%85%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6/%E5%BE%AA%E7%8E%AF%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85/%E5%BF%83%E8%82%8C%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85/</link><pubDate>Sat, 19 Nov 2022 14:25:51 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://daisilia.com/series/%E5%86%85%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6/%E5%BE%AA%E7%8E%AF%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85/%E5%BF%83%E8%82%8C%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85/</guid><description/></item><item><title>心脏瓣膜疾病</title><link>https://daisilia.com/series/%E5%86%85%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6/%E5%BE%AA%E7%8E%AF%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85/%E5%BF%83%E8%84%8F%E7%93%A3%E8%86%9C%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85/</link><pubDate>Sat, 19 Nov 2022 14:24:48 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://daisilia.com/series/%E5%86%85%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6/%E5%BE%AA%E7%8E%AF%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85/%E5%BF%83%E8%84%8F%E7%93%A3%E8%86%9C%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85/</guid><description/></item><item><title>心包疾病</title><link>https://daisilia.com/series/%E5%86%85%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6/%E5%BE%AA%E7%8E%AF%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85/%E5%BF%83%E5%8C%85%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85/</link><pubDate>Sat, 19 Nov 2022 14:26:40 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://daisilia.com/series/%E5%86%85%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6/%E5%BE%AA%E7%8E%AF%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85/%E5%BF%83%E5%8C%85%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85/</